Title: Detection Hub – Self‑Service Installation Pipeline on SCP 

Objective 

Build a self‑service deployment pipeline (SCP pattern) to install/upgrade Detection Hub Helm charts across environments with standardized controls, auditable changes, and minimal manual intervention. 

Scope 

CI/CD pipeline to run Helm upgrade --install against AKS clusters for Detection Hub. 

Parameterized by environment & namespace.(find or create) 

Secure handling of secrets (ACR cred, app passwords). 

Pre‑checks (namespace, quotas, PDB rules) and post‑deploy health checks. 

Rollback on failure; deployment report artifact. 

Background 

Manual install has been validated in dev: 

Shell 

helm upgrade --install -n dev-dethub dethub symphonyfs/detectionhub --version 0.1.0 
 

 

